        "description": "Validation uses the identical FDA GCBP geometry and the same five flow-speed operating points that constitute the COU decision space. Fluid properties, rotational speed range (2500–4500 RPM), and flow range (3–6 L/min) are within the COU operating envelope. No extrapolation beyond validated regime required. Gradation 2 satisfied."
